    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and finely dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>thyme leaves </strong>from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-6-1688140466529-x200.jpg",
