    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through, then drain and return to the pot with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and <strong>mint sauce</strong></p><p>Mix it all together – these are your <strong>minted peas</strong></p>",
